The new Algolia, Elasticsearch and Typesense alternative is in town! Introducing Meilisearch
&ldquo;Meilisearch is a powerful, fast, open-source, easy to use and deploy search engine. Both searching and indexing are highly customizable. Features such as typo-tolerance, filters, and synonyms are provided out-of-the-box.&rdquo;
In this article, I want to share &ldquo;How to set up meilisearch in ubuntu for production&rdquo;
